value: Breeds from the middle Mackenzie Valley and Lake Athabaska to west- ern Ontario and south (east of the Cascades) to Oregon, Utah and Ne- braska; formerly to northern Illinois. Winters chiefly from the southern United States south to Panama and the West Indies.
